==English==

===Preposition===

{{en-prep}}

# Thirty minutes past a certain hour.
#: ''We'll meet up at '''half past''' five.''

===Noun===
{{en-noun|-}}

# [[thirty|Thirty]] [[minute]]s past any [[hour]].
#: ''My train's supposed to arrive at 2. Let's plan on meeting at '''half past'''.''

